{
  "id": "adv_event_2308_01_01",
  "title": "トリは\nトリエル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん……うち、フェスには出られません\nステージに上がる資格、うちにはもうないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… I can't perform at the festival.\nI don't have the right to stand on stage anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.8220182418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "責任感の強い、優らしい考え方だけど\n……考え直してくれないか、優",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a very responsible way of thinking‚ Yu‚ but…\n…can you reconsider‚ Yu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0333333333,
      "endTime": 17.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.7410430713
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.5663262685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_04-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ！　これまで一緒に頑張ってきたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! We've worked so hard together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5663262685,
      "endTime": 21.032991822499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "お願い、そんなこと言わないで！\n優ちゃんがいないなんて嫌だよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don't say that!\nI don't want you to be gone‚ Yu-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2329919179,
      "endTime": 27.5651007016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.7663252513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、うん……。でも、ダメなんや\nうちがステージに立てば、みんなに迷惑が掛かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah… But I can't.\nIf I stand on stage‚ I'll be a burden to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7663252513,
      "endTime": 36.792833391900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.9996585846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな風に終わっちゃうなんて……私、嫌だよっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want it to end like this… I hate it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9996585846,
      "endTime": 41.8737175942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.0663252513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_04-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、みんな、ごめん……。ほんまに許して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ everyone‚ I'm really sorry… Please forgive me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.0663252513,
      "endTime": 48.260590903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこんなことになってしまったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did it come to this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4663280487,
      "endTime": 51.4846953869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4846954823,
      "endTime": 53.6246955157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6246955157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……いいステージが出来たわ\n今日の会場も満席だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That was a great stage.\nToday's venue was full too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5846959909,
      "endTime": 58.8500246843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0513626576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "地方の大きな会場でもチケットは完売みたいだし\nこのところ、ますますファンが増えたみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the tickets for the big local venues are sold out.\nIt seems like our fans are increasing more and more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0513626576,
      "endTime": 66.1250814915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3180293243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　私達のファンは日本中に\nたっっっくさんいるんだもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! We have a lot of fans\nall over Japan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3180293243,
      "endTime": 71.9380294959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロにいた頃より確実にステップアップしてんなぁ\n星見プロは、まだまだ規模は小さいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've definitely stepped up since our days at Van Prods.\nHoshimi Prods is still small‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1513626576,
      "endTime": 79.63294987680001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8180293243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ガッツとアイデア勝負じゃバンプロに負けてへんし\nTRINITYAiLEは今、いい波に乗れとるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but we have guts and ideas.\nTRINITYAiLE is riding a good wave right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8180293243,
      "endTime": 87.6122696083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8180293243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "これも{user}さん達のおかげね\n返しきれないくらいのご恩を受けてしまったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's thanks to {user}-san and the team.\nWe've received so much we can't repay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8180293243,
      "endTime": 93.7656027953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9513626576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "恩返しの方法ならあるやん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is a way to repay them‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9513626576,
      "endTime": 96.3013626099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "なになに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4846959909,
      "endTime": 97.74345440469999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0847071807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "それはな、うちらが星見プロ二組目の\nBIG4になればいいんや。今のうちらなら、狙えるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to become Hoshimi Pro's second BIG4.\nWe can aim for it with our current momentum.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0847071807,
      "endTime": 106.5447976271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7513738473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん。そしたら{user}さんは\n日本一の名マネージャーさんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. Then {user}-san will be\nthe best manager in Japan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7513738473,
      "endTime": 113.165274032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3513738473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロ二組目のBIG4\n私達三人で、絶対になってみせる。頑張りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Prods's second BIG4.\nThe three of us will definitely make it happen. Let's work hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3513738473,
      "endTime": 121.1195144494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3847061634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "おー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3847061634,
      "endTime": 122.7846954823,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1766.6559855999963
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.655985600002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3033.322652199999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、ライブ良かったよ\n……って、随分盛り上がってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great job‚ the live was good.\n…Seems like you're all pretty excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6847076893,
      "endTime": 130.9430521489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.1430522442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　{user}さんはモテモテって話やん\n二人ともマネージャーさんが大好きって知ってた～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I heard {user}-san is quite popular.\nDid y'all know both of you love our manager?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1430522442,
      "endTime": 139.3497414112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.5430522442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
